{"tid":268903,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 點樣令到呀哥同佢女朋友分手","createTime":"2017-06-03T11:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T11:54:27.000Z","uid":14779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d4711caad2780f9b1677e35fb5574050821f98","tid":268903,"uid":14779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上次都講過個八婆用手袋𠝹花咗我架車<br />\n呢單嘢我都算數啦當比面呀哥<br />\n直至琴晚，個八婆上嚟屋企食飯，咁我都打算食完都會車佢返屋企架啦<br />\n點知個八婆食完飯就坐係梳化到un un腳，hea到11點左右，個八婆話要返屋企啦終於<br />\n呀哥就係咁意問我怕唔怕攰，如果攰大佬可以call uber送佢返屋企喎 (我住清水灣，個八婆住天水圍)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 八婆， <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀哥， <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<br />\n八婆：吓，車我返屋企唔係must嚟架咩？鬼叫你冇車牌咩 搞到我要你個寶貝細妹車我返屋企<br />\n<br />\n呀哥：對唔住呀bb，我排緊期考牌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n八婆： 你估我好想坐你個妹車？ 揸埋啲日本車<br />\n<br />\n我： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...... 心諗咪坐呀笨 你咪又係買唔起<br />\n<br />\n車佢返屋企個程路佢不斷咁&quot;㗩㗩聲&quot;，又話咩坐唔穩又話乜嘢垃圾車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我嬲得濟掉底咗佢係元朗啲山卡啦地方，我咁樣掉底佢佢都仲未同我呀哥講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6979c398f6994c70e26c0f3b584a74f4beb8b715","tid":268903,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"溝咗佢女朋友"},{"pid":"87b59c5c3ea7e147df89017ebedbc52e15684ffe","tid":268903,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"同老竇老母呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa04d69353dd88646aa731f803053c1d49e3a941","tid":268903,"uid":14779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溝咗佢女朋友</blockquote><br />\n我係女 就算我係仔都唔會溝件八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f8f04cb91eb8d27d21ac9ea2ebd2d98b004aa5","tid":268903,"uid":34392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"住清水灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可唔可以溝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47f673e5ad6cf9e63848db811cb10598fb45dd0","tid":268903,"uid":94151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"假膠？"},{"pid":"cd14215a2b9029a0589fd1b1e6502070c26a6fe9","tid":268903,"uid":14779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住清水灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我可唔可以溝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我住淺水灣你先溝我啦"},{"pid":"1825c5854669333a7f5189fcb155860670365e3d","tid":268903,"uid":22755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"你點解要車佢 你根本唔洗理佢"},{"pid":"4ae12bc3514a39590d2bc48f098b78f6b2e97042","tid":268903,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"見到樓豬個名就知點解你咁想你呀哥分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6b8b4d2a3de903ec30c88cfa98baca30685d0c","tid":268903,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"做你阿哥女朋友"},{"pid":"d51ec25c6188e57d438fca209b3e7477ec679916","tid":268903,"uid":14779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到樓豬個名就知點解你咁想你呀哥分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as